{"id":35671,"name":"Buzzkill: Hide \"Like\", \"Tweet\", and \"+1\" buttons","category":"global","raw_subcategory":null,"subcategory":null,"style_tags":[],"description":"<p><strong>Enjoy a cleaner, less cluttered reading experience on your favorite blogs and news sites.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bloggers are going nuts with all of the sharing icons at the end of their posts -- cluttering up the screen with buttons of all different shapes and sizes, and channeling web design practices from 1999. Buzzkill hides the Facebook \"Like\" button, the Google \"+1\" button, the Twitter \"Tweet\" button, the Tweetmeme \"retweet\" button, and tons of other social sharing buttons that you never use.</p>","user":{"id":59608,"name":"papermodelplane","email":"redacted","paypal_email":null,"homepage":null,"about":null,"license":null},"admin_delete_reason_id":null,"updated":"2012-09-11T17:54:05.000Z","weekly_install_count":0,"total_install_count":674,"rating":null,"screenshot_url":"https://userstyles.org/style_screenshots/35671_after.jpeg?r=1589270581","url":"/styles/35671/buzzkill-hide-like-tweet-and-1-buttons","discussionsCount":1,"commentsCount":2,"css":"#fb-like, .facebook-like, .fb-like-button, .fb_share_link, #fbShare, .fbshare, a[name=fb_share], .fbConnectWidgetTopmost, .post-fb-like, .wdt_button.wdt_fb, #facebook .pluginCountButton, #facebook .pluginSubscribe, .widget .btn-o, .widget #c, #widget .btn-o, #widget #c, #root #plusone, .social-stub.facebook, .social-stub.twitter, .social-stub.googleplus, .social-stub.linkedin, .social_button.twitter_button, .social_button.facebook_button, #sticky_sharing, .inline_sharing, #___plus_0, #___plusone_0, #___plusone_1, #___plusone_2, .google-buzz-button, #tweet-button, .twitter-share-button, .twitter-follow-button, .tweet-this, .connect_widget, .IN-widget, .db-wrapper, .DiggThisButton, .share_reddit, #tip_techmeme, #neatoButton, .a2a_dd, .addthis_default_style, .addthis_toolbox, .addthis_button_pinterest, .addthis_button_stumbleupon, .aol-s